## 7. How the System Works (Short)

- **RAG**: Combines retrieval from a PDF knowledge base with LLM generation to give grounded answers.[web:16][web:20]
- **ChromaDB**: Stores text chunks and their embeddings to support fast similarity search.[web:20][web:22]
- **LangGraph**: Orchestrates the RAG workflow as a graph with a process node and output node, and maintains state for each query.[web:9][web:10][web:19]
- **HITL**: Escalates low-confidence or sensitive queries to a human who can override or approve the model‚Äôs answer.[web:15][web:21][web:23]

